  <brief_title>A Postural Study Comparing Sitting on the Floor Versus Sitting in a Chair While Playing Video Games.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Postural Analysis of Children Playing Video Games Sitting on the Floor vs. Sitting in a Chair: A Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Glinn and Giordano Physical Therapy</agency>
